@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uiyslg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v0 + 0.36) / (v0 + 0.06 * v1 + 0.45)))
    v2 = (v0 * v1)
    v0 = (tmp - wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.04)))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v0 + 0.17) + v2))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = (0.61 / 0.15)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v2 + 0.11) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.08)))
    data[tid] = v0
